@host = http://localhost:8080
@base = {{host}}/api

### 1) 注册成功
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1001",
  "educationEmail": "test1001@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 2) 用户名重复（预期：业务异常）
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1002",
  "educationEmail": "test1002@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 3) 邮箱重复（预期：业务异常）
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test2",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1003",
  "educationEmail": "test1001@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 4) 登录成功（预期：code=0，data 为 LoginVO 对象）
POST {{base}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

 {
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5) 登录失败（预期：code=405，message=密码错误，data=null）
POST {{base}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

 {
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "1234567"
}
